Japan Death Toll Hits 6,911, Surpassing 1995 Kobe Earthquake, NHK Reports

-- B y   N a t a l i e   O b i k o   P e a r s o n
-- 
2011-03-18T15:23:13Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-18/japan-death-toll-hits-6-911-surpassing-1995-kobe-earthquake-nhk-reports.html
  Japan ’s official death toll from
last week’s earthquake and tsunami has risen to 6,911,
surpassing the 6,434 fatalities caused by the 1995 Kobe
earthquake, NHK reported, citing police figures.  To contact the reporter on this story:
